Title: People often give "emptying a dishwasher" as an example of a task AI can't do yet but people can't d...
Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: People often give "emptying a dishwasher" as an example of a task AI can't do yet but people can't do this task either. Have you ever tried to empty someone else's or have someone empty yours? Every other item is like "uuuuh, where does this one go?"
